+sub_section( 'Menu item image', 'menu-image' )
	p If you want to display an image in the menu item (useful in <a href="#megamenu">megamenu</a>), insert it as an inline image into the menu item label, and set "<strong>Is image</strong>" block style for the menu item:

	ol
		li Select the menu item where you want to insert an image.

		li
			p Click the "<strong>More</strong>" dropdown button from the block toolbar options and select "<strong>Inline image</strong>".

			+image( 'menu-image-1.jpg', 'Inserting inline image into menu item' )

		li Choose the image to insert into the menu item.

		li
			p Optionally apply the "<strong>Is image</strong>" block style onto the menu item. It will adapt the image width in the menu.

			+image( 'menu-image-2.jpg', 'Applying "Is image" menu item block style' )
